{"tid":543249,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《與神同行》電子鍋掀熱潮  網友搶購歡慶台票房破4億大放送","createTime":"2018-01-28T10:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T22:51:01.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac0afcfc4a2a9ced3c6f43c10744b2467f94d19","tid":543249,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"韓片《與神同行》日前以3.5億台幣打敗《屍速列車》在台票房，截至昨日為止，正式突破4億成績，坐穩台灣韓片票房的冠軍寶座。電影中，除了金秀鴻與媽媽告別的橋段讓人落淚，其中男主角買電子鍋想送給媽媽的畫面，也成為觀眾津津樂道的名場面之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5a6af0c8b9b21a52f4d1e371_201801261711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5a6af0c8b9b21a52f4d1e371_201801261711.jpg&h=1cd87f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲電影中，金自鴻來不及把電鍋送給媽媽的橋段惹哭不少觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n改編自同名漫畫的《與神同行》，片中金自鴻（車太鉉 飾）因兒時愛吃媽媽煮的鍋巴飯，長大有能力賺錢後，偷偷買了電子鍋想送給母親，但因為年少不懂事的舉動，讓他遲遲不敢送豐田 HIACE「堅‧實力派」全面升級至歐盟 6 型動力系統出去，結果還未親手交給母親，他就因公殉職，最後由江林公子（河正宇 飾）替他完成心願。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ipHcX006dyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FipHcX006dyQ&d=LlKYsBJqCa29R27Wx8rYi9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=70c518e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ipHcX006dyQ</a><br />\n▲電影中造成搶購的電子鍋曾找宋仲基代言。<br />\n<br />\n這成功賺走觀眾眼淚的橋段，讓網友紛紛表示看到電子鍋就會想到劇情而落淚。劇中的電子鍋也因電影的加持瞬間爆紅，不少商家還為此推出類似產品，成功造成搶購熱潮，而電影中的產品牌子「CUCHEN」也曾找過宋仲基代言。《與神同行》台灣片商為了感謝觀眾支持，將贈送2個電子鍋回饋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5a6af0c9da68fc5330824e4e_201801261711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5a6af0c9da68fc5330824e4e_201801261711.jpg&h=c59f6cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲除了催淚的電子鍋橋段，金秀鴻與母親淚別畫面也感動不少人。"},{"pid":"70fbfa6cfaaa9ac8bcbc5c6b0e3342127ead7ba3","tid":543249,"uid":142233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"68d1bd2e9cf9c421e961a574bad91e2b11b66af4","tid":543249,"uid":48,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"台灣人真係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d2a137cb9a749951d0983932679d9b4cd8c0ba","tid":543249,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d1bd2e9cf9c421e961a574bad91e2b11b66af4","tid":543249,"uid":48,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"台灣人真係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897ffbcb17e94a08a24c4e73467ee9504fcc883a","tid":543249,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T21:57:43.000Z","msg":"完全錯撚曬重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f825eb891383f0b8bbff4bb526837513eec7bbb5","tid":543249,"uid":1452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T22:23:37.000Z","msg":"真係咁好睇？"},{"pid":"a670f1649a1c0986407badbebbe3c5e50e13aa72","tid":543249,"uid":50063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T22:51:01.000Z","msg":"到底係想送貨車定電子鍋？"}]}